query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 acc q1 s t1 tq1 u1 b) */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from tag_question AS tq1
inner join question AS q1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.score >= 0 AND q1.score <= 5
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('crossfilter',
'fgets',
'filenotfoundexception',
'font-size',
'look-and-feel',
'nopcommerce',
'nsfetchrequest',
'progress',
'public-key-encryption',
'repaint',
'xor')
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.reputation >= 0 AND u1.reputation <= 10
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Autobiographer',
'Custodian',
'Informed',
'Student',
'Tumbleweed') group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
